title: Sample Book, The Finest in Wallpaper, 1953–54
medium: machine-printed, lithography, and screen printed on paper

description: "A Wallpaper collection that mirrors the spirit of our 13 original states..." Printed by machine, lithography and silk screen. Includes "Williamsburg Restoration Reproductions" and "Williamsburg Restoration Commemorative Paper Hangings." Twenty designs with color alternates.
